OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779225068
OL,3,CSummerland families challenge Attorney
OL,4,CGeneral's decision to deny new inquest
OL,6,FCampaigners calling for a fresh
OL,7,Finquest into the 1973 Summerland fire
OL,8,Fdisaster have travelled to the Isle of
OL,9,FMan, to challenge the Attorney
OL,10,FGeneral's decision to deny a new
OL,11,Finquiry.
OL,13,FThe Summerland families are set to
OL,14,Fattend a two-day hearing at Douglas
OL,15,FCourthouse, where their legal team
OL,16,Fwill challenge Walter Wannenburgh's
OL,17,Fdecision.
OL,19,FChair of the campaign Jackie Hallam
OL,20,Fwas caught in the fire aged 13 and
OL,21,Flost her mum Lorna and her friend Jane.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779225068
OL,3,CSummerland families challenge Attorney
OL,4,CGeneral's decision to deny new inquest
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the hearing, she
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's the only thing left that I
OL,8,Fcan do for my mum and my friend.
OL,10,F"What else can I do what else can I do
OL,11,Fbut to right this terrible misjustice?
OL,12,FAnd I will carry on and until my dying
OL,13,Fday, if necessary to to challenge this
OL,14,Fand to put it right."
OL,16,FIn March 2025, the 'Justice for
OL,17,FSummerland' group made an application
OL,18,Fto the Attorney General, asking for a
OL,19,Ffresh inquest to be held.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779225068
OL,3,CSummerland families challenge Attorney
OL,4,CGeneral's decision to deny new inquest
OL,6,FBy May the same year, Manx Attorney
OL,7,FGeneral Walter Wannenburgh concluded
OL,8,Fdue to a lack of 'fresh evidence', he
OL,9,Fwas unable to agree to a new
OL,10,Finvestigation, describing the original
OL,11,Finquiry as 'thorough, effective and
OL,12,Fproportionate'.
OL,14,FA total of 50 people lost their lives
OL,15,Fin the Summerland fire in 1973, with
OL,16,Fmany more injured as a result of the
OL,17,Fblaze.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779225068
OL,3,CSummerland families challenge Attorney
OL,4,CGeneral's decision to deny new inquest
OL,6,FA verdict of misadventure was given to
OL,7,Fthose who died, which the campaign
OL,8,Fgroup says puts the blame on the
OL,9,Fvictims.
OL,11,FJane Stevenson lost her grandmother in
OL,12,Fthe fire, and said her father was
OL,13,F'devastated' at the original verdict
OL,14,Fwhen he came to identify her body.
OL,16,FShe said: "I lost my father just over
OL,17,Ftwo weeks ago. He kept so quiet about
OL,18,Fthe events of 1973, because it
OL,19,Faffected him so badly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779225068
OL,3,CSummerland families challenge Attorney
OL,4,CGeneral's decision to deny new inquest
OL,6,F"But once he knew that we had this
OL,7,Fcampaign, and that I wanted to be
OL,8,Finvolved, he started to open up, and
OL,9,Fhe talked so much about it then -
OL,10,Fslowly at first - but I think it
OL,11,Fhelped him.
OL,13,F"I'm so sad that he will not be here
OL,14,Fto get to the hopefully the end of the
OL,15,Fnew inquest, but he knew we were doing
OL,16,Fsomething, and so that certainly
OL,17,Fdrives me on even more."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
