OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779225068
OL,3,CSummerland families challenge Attorney
OL,4,CGeneral's decision to deny new inquest
OL,6,FEarlier this year, the families
OL,7,Ftravelled to Westminster, where they
OL,8,Fmet with a number of MPs showing their
OL,9,Fsupport for a fresh inquest.
OL,11,FLiverpool West Derby's Ian Byrne, and
OL,12,FWarrington South's Sarah Hall, held a
OL,13,Fmeeting with survivors, where they
OL,14,Fstarted plans for a delegation to
OL,15,Ftravel to the island.
OL,17,FWhile in Westminster, members of the
OL,18,Fcampaign also met with justice
OL,19,Fminister Jake Richards MP - a key
OL,20,Fpolitical figure in the context of the
OL,21,FIsle of Man.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779225068
OL,3,CSummerland families challenge Attorney
OL,4,CGeneral's decision to deny new inquest
OL,6,FUnder his role as Parliamentary Under-
OL,7,FSecretary of State within the Ministry
OL,8,Fof Justice, his remit involves
OL,9,Fexamining the UK Government's
OL,10,Frelationship with the island,
OL,11,Falongside other Crown Dependencies.
OL,13,FWriting on X after meeting with the
OL,14,Fgroup, Mr Richards said: "Important to
OL,15,Fmeet the Summerland Campaign Group
OL,16,Ftoday - with fellow MPs supporting
OL,17,Ftheir constituents.
OL,19,F"These determined and inspiring women
OL,20,Fare fighting for answers, and I will
OL,21,Fplay my part in helping them."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779225068
OL,3,CSummerland families challenge Attorney
OL,4,CGeneral's decision to deny new inquest
OL,6,FThe campaigners are being represented
OL,7,Fby human rights lawyer, Harry Robinson
OL,8,Ffrom Phoenix Law who are based in
OL,9,FBelfast.
OL,11,FWhen asked why they deem it
OL,12,Fappropriate to seek a fresh inquest,
OL,13,FMr Robinson said: "The purpose of
OL,14,Finquests is not only to return facts
OL,15,Fabout any kind of death, but also to
OL,16,Fallay rumour and suspicion, and to
OL,17,Fprovide families and loved ones with
OL,18,Fenough information to make clear how a
OL,19,Fdeath has come to pass.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779225068
OL,3,CSummerland families challenge Attorney
OL,4,CGeneral's decision to deny new inquest
OL,6,F"Also to draw from any particular
OL,7,Fdeath, anything that can be learned to
OL,8,Fprotect people in the future.
OL,10,F"In losing somebody and experiencing
OL,11,Fgrief, you think about that person all
OL,12,Fthe time, and to have that hanging
OL,13,Fover you, coupled with the size and
OL,14,Fscale of this devastating disaster,
OL,15,Fcould be a real challenge and,
OL,16,Fburdensome for the families to bear
OL,17,Ffor so many years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779225068
OL,3,CSummerland families challenge Attorney
OL,4,CGeneral's decision to deny new inquest
OL,6,F"So they have some unanswered
OL,7,Fquestions that were certainly not
OL,8,Fanswered by the inquest at the time,
OL,9,Fand a fresh inquest would be the
OL,10,Fmechanism to, unearth some more facts
OL,11,Fand fully examine and ventilate, all
OL,12,Fof the facts as related to the deaths
OL,13,Fat the time."
OL,15,FThe Isle of Man Government has been
OL,16,Fcontacted for comment.
OL,18,FThe hearing is set to get underway at
OL,19,FDouglas Courthouse at 10am on
OL,20,FWednesday 20 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
